headline: US is only country debating GLP-1 insurance coverage for weight loss: Cigna CEO Cordani
summary: Cigna (CI) CEO David Cordani is not convinced of the benefits of GLP-1s for weight-loss patients and said the US is the only country among developed nations where insurance coverage is being debated.

headline: Judge dismisses lawsuit against Wells Fargo over prescription drug costs
summary: The decision could throw cold water on potential copycat suits seeking to hold large, self-funded employers responsible if they overpay for prescription drugs.
